ate approach is essential in all interactions. Improving Lives : The NHS aims to improve the lives of patients and communities. Working Together for Patients : Collaboration and teamwork are emphasized. Everyone Counts : All individuals matter in the NHS Course Overview Adult Nursing", "english_requirement": {"ielts": null}}, "metadata": {"url": "https://icp.navitas.com/study/undergraduate/nursing/", "scraped_at": "2026-04-26T10:24:24.457974+00:00"}},
